{"_id":"qvzQlvZGQHceu2Dm","name":"Mental Mark (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx]{Magic Hack}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl40_LabelName\">When an enemy fails a Will save against one of your technomancer spells, it takes a –2 penalty to saving throws and AC for 1 round. When an enemy succeeds at a Will save against one of your technomancer spells, it takes a –1 penalty to saving throws against your spells for 1 round. A creature can take only one penalty from a mental mark at a time.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Technomancer","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":null,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":null,"shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":null,"additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"8th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"rDCdrOBeaaeFLjmg","name":"Enhanced Senses (Ex; Drone)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"mod","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.QsCRXffpsDoMvPnT]{Basic Mods}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl07_LabelName\">Your drone gains low-light vision, darkvision to 60 feet, and a +2 insight bonus to Perception skill checks. If your drone has the camera mod, the camera gains these senses as well.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","type":"","modifiers":[{"name":"New Modifier","modifier":2,"type":"insight","effectType":"skill","valueAffected":"per","enabled":true,"source":"","notes":"","modifierType":"constant","condition":"","subtab":"misc","_id":"8cfd3643-78d0-4e68-9d47-f113eea04f2a"}],"maxInstalls":1,"additionalMovement":"","arms":{"number":0,"armType":"general"},"isArmorSlot":false,"weaponProficiency":"","additionalSenses":"low-light vision 60; darkvision 60","bonusSkill":"","damage":{"parts":[]},"critical":{"parts":[]},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"rEN2qQAKD2d5jd2n","name":"Medication Mastery (Ex)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.rpaon3jF3nCe5eP9]{Theorem (Ex)}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You can quickly turn the compounds and catalysts in your custom microlab into medicinals. You can create an analgesic, an antitoxin, or a sedative with an item level no higher than your biohacker level. If you are an instinctive biohacker, you can also make excitants and stimulants. If you are a studious biohacker, you can also make antiemetics and coagulants. These medicinals are highly unstable and cannot be stored for later use or used by anyone else. You can add one of these medicinals to any attack you make with an injection weapon as part of the action to make the attack or attacks, but you can’t add a biohack of any kind to the same attack. You can use this ability a number of times equal to your key ability score, and you regain all expended uses of this ability (up to your maximum) when you take a 10-minute rest to recover Stamina Points.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Theorem","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"2nd Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"rEZt5hlJTC9BJj5D","name":"Phase Shot (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx]{Magic Hack}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl54_LabelName\">As a standard action, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to fire a single shot from a ranged weapon at a target known to you within range. The shot travels straight to the target, passing through any nonmagical barrier in its way, ignoring hardness and Hit Points (any magical barrier, such as a <em>wall of force</em>, stops the shot). This ability negates cover and concealment modifiers, but otherwise the attack is rolled normally.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Technomancer","type":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":"","units":""},"target":{"value":"","type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"none","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"none","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"14th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
