{"_id":"rTaxnu0ObdXF13Sk","name":"Weapon Specialization (Ex) (Mystic)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.classes.bItuvukGHbObTApr]{Mystic}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListClasses_ctl00_LabelName\">You gain @Compendium[sfrpg.feats.9Us7Eg9cAoq3BcS5]{Weapon Specialization (Combat)}&nbsp;as a bonus feat for each weapon type this class grants you proficiency with.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Mystic","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"3rd Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"roUznc0mBdn1yDBT","name":"Entropic Charge (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">When you charge, you can attempt any combat maneuver for which you have the Improved Combat Maneuver feat in place of the normal melee attack. In addition, you can forgo gaining an Entropy Point for charging to ignore the normal charge penalties to your attack and AC, and to gain the ability to charge through difficult terrain.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Vanguard Dscipline","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"6th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"rpaon3jF3nCe5eP9","name":"Theorem (Ex)","permission":{"default":0},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.classes.PSHcGB4UFgMSiF4V]{Biohacker}</p>\n<p>As you gain experience, you devise theories about the way the universe works. Some theorems you can apply to yourself, altering your physiological structure to gain specific benefits, while others require the use of your custom microlab or other equipment or add additional options for your biohacks.<br><br>You learn your first theorem at 2nd level, and you gain an additional theorem every 2 levels thereafter. If a theorem allows an opponent a saving throw to resist its effects, the DC is equal to 10 + half your biohacker level + your key ability score modifier. If a theorem requires an opponent to attempt a skill check, the DC is equal to 10 + 1-1/2 × your biohacker level + your key ability score modifier. Unless otherwise specified, you can’t learn a theorem more than once. Once you learn a theorem, that choice cannot be changed.</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_Header\">Theorems all require you to have a minimum biohacker level and are organized accordingly. Some theorems require you to satisfy other prerequisites, such as knowing other theorems.<br><br>Theorems marked with an asterisk (*) apply to your biohacks class feature and do not stack with one another. Only one such theorem can be applied to an individual biohack.</span></p>\n<h2>2nd Level</h2>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You must be 2nd level or higher to choose these theorems.</span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.2wQesgqQYCpSuuoI]{Field Dressing (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.AQW8PuTemku5dbwA]{Hampering Inhibitor* (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.rEN2qQAKD2d5jd2n]{Medication Mastery (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.yXyV06BabbFy7aNz]{Painful Injection (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.spy4ryqEuDGEqlyW]{Speedy Serums (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.XSQIDmPCYPmFvEfU]{Toxic Skin (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.QrBp9JextzHKSFPU]{Treat Condition (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.TguNcpqReCw2GpAZ]{Treatment Mastery (Ex)}</p>\n<h2 class=\"title\">8th Level</h2>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You must be 8th level or higher to choose these theorems.</span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.HJ7rwsCh1ge3odiy]{Arms Expert (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.lqCOwgr4f81UKsMk]{Far Injection (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.INOTRXWmdHya6rxJ]{Improved Treat Condition (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.bq2rYuc1baPTFYDA]{Powerful Biohacks* (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.Si9wJXBRsK4URfhO]{Stable Biohacks (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.xzgaMDPHmoQ7Fvqh]{Tranq Dart (Ex)}</p>\n<h2 class=\"title\">14th Level</h2>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You must be 14th level or higher to choose these theorems.</span></p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.lKy2oZHD0yNqSwu3]{Energetic Booster* (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.b70jMxyndkJy5hg7]{Greater Field Dressing (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.s72Xfh5yucrGObR3]{Greater Treat Condition (Ex)}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.17edcwnnoKQo9dx1]{Liquid Bravery (Ex)}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Biohacker","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"2nd Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"s2666UOaMcZCw251","name":"Reaction","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.wq8dRJYQ58VZQuZU]{First Vanguard Aspect}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You embody the change entropy brings about through biological, chemical, and molecular reactions, such as rust and rot.<br><br>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.SvjHeYcqBNY1lcDH]{Reaction Insight (Ex)} You gain Improved Combat Maneuver (dirty trick) as a bonus feat and a +2 insight bonus to Physical Science checks.<br><br>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.vsa43Qyn1o8QvOJx]{Reaction Embodiment (Su)} Once per combat, when you impose a condition on an enemy, you can gain 1 Entropy Point without taking any additional action.<br><br>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.E6P58sWAhk0wZ21s]{Reaction Catalyst (Su)} Each foe within 30 feet must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw or gain the sickened condition for 1 round per vanguard level.<br><br><em>Improved</em>: One target of your choice within this ability’s range is also nauseated for 1 round if it fails its Fortitude save.<br><br>@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.dGkszY4TiOZ9kfNS]{Reaction Finale (Su)} You can spend 2 Entropy Points as a reaction to expose a creature you injure to entropic toxin. The save DC is determined as normal for an aspect ability. Once you apply this poison to a target, the target is immune to further applications of your entropic toxin for 24 hours. </span></p>\n<h3 class=\"title\">Entropic Toxin</h3>\n<p><strong>Type</strong> poison (injury, special); <strong>Save</strong> Fortitude (DC varies)<br><strong>Track</strong> choose Strength, Dexterity, Constitution, Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma (special); <strong>Frequency</strong> 1/round for 3 rounds<br><strong>Effect</strong> The target cannot progress beyond impaired/stiffened on the progression track.<br><strong>Cure</strong> 1 save</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Vanguard Aspect","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"2nd Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"s72Xfh5yucrGObR3","name":"Greater Treat Condition (Ex)","permission":{"default":0,"QqVQDajn5ZN4kl25":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.rpaon3jF3nCe5eP9]{Theorem (Ex)}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">Add the following conditions to the list of those you can remove with the treat condition theorem: cowering, dazed, panicked, paralyzed, and stunned. You must know the treat condition and improved treat condition theorems to select this theorem.</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Theorem","type":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"area":{"value":null,"units":"","shape":"","effect":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","additional":"","per":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"parts":[],"effect":""},"damage":{"parts":[]},"formula":"","save":{"type":"","dc":null,"descriptor":""},"descriptors":[],"modifiers":[],"requirements":"14th Level","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"abilityMods":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
